name: Martina Jalloud
description: I am a single girl who is looking for that perfect love in my life. I am a God fearing person who knows what I want in life. I live by the fruits of the spirit, love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, gentleness, humility, faithfulness and self-control. I am not conceited nor envious and I do not like arguments or fights so I believe a couple should be able to settle any disagreements peacefully. I also live by the Golden Rule that we treat one another as we would want to be treated. I am a girl who will always cherish, love and respect my partner to the highest degree and I am looking for that man to return these same things to me. I will walk with you in this life and into eternity.. If you think you are the one that God has sent for me
